<table width=75%>
<tr><td bgcolor="#0000AF">
<strong><font color=white>
<center>Totemic Gauntlets Quest</center>
</font></strong>
</td></tr>
</table><BR>
<div align="left">
1) Talk to Vrynn in Lake Rathetear.<BR>
<BR>
2) Collect the following and give them to Vrynn to receive your Totemic Gauntlets.<BR>
<BR>
- Banded Gauntlets (must be medium size)<BR>
- 1 Crushed Dufrenite<BR>
- Mammoth's Rib Bone (Everfrost)<BR>
- Griffene Downfeather (North Karana)</div>
<BR>
<table width=100% cellspacing=10>
<tr><td width=50% bgcolor="#0000AF">
