<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Anteil</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-06-20 15:23:13</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Getting the Mammoth Rib is a pain.  For starters, I can track.  You would think 'Good he can track the Wooly Mammoths'.  Half right.  Both Wooly Mammoths and Wooly Mammoth Calfs show up as "Wooly Mammoth" on track, so most everything on track are calves.  I have only killed 4 or 5 Mammoths (they aren't common but haven't really seen how common either)  They are green to me at 35 and can take about a bubble of my 1100hp before they're dead.  I have yet to see a location shouted with a dead Mammoth =(</font></td></tr></table>
