<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Bowmor (24 Barb Shammie)</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-07-12 18:13:10</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>I responded to a shout in Everfrost to get my Mammoth Rib.<BR>
There were two shouts within three hours so these are not<BR>
that hard to come by.<BR>
The Dufrenite is expensive and I can see that it will be a<BR>
gating factor in the quest for most of the totemic pieces.<BR>
The griffenne (NK)requires killing griffawns in order to get<BR>
them to spawn.  Last night with the indispensable help <BR>
of a ranger to track them, and my back to the Woodbridge<BR>
zone, in case Grimfeathers showed up, after a couple of <BR>
solid hunting hours a Downfeather was finally dropped.<BR>
Tonight I off for Lake Rathe to find the ogre who will <BR>
"crush crush crush" the Dufie for me so I can find Vrynn.<BR>
</font></td></tr></table>
